#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:872
msgid ""
"Additional FFmpeg arguments for snapshot generation. Common options: -"
"hwaccel none, -hwaccel auto, -hwaccel vaapi (for Intel GPU)"
msgstr ""
"生成快照时传递给 FFmpeg 的额外参数。常用选项：-hwaccel none（无硬件加速）、-"
"hwaccel auto（自动）、-hwaccel vaapi（Intel GPU）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:464
msgid "Advanced Interface Settings"
msgstr "高级接口设置"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:736
