msgstr "访问日志格式"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:803
msgid "Access Log Path"
msgstr "访问日志路径"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:348
msgid "Auto restart after crash"
msgstr "程序崩溃后自动重启"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:331
msgid "Basic Settings"
msgstr "基础设置"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:564
msgid "Buffer Pool Max Size"
msgstr "缓冲池最大容量"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:780
msgid "CORS Allow Origin"
msgstr "CORS 允许的源"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:367
msgid "Config File Content"
msgstr "配置文件内容"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:465
msgid "Configure separate interfaces for multicast, FCC and RTSP"
msgstr "分别配置组播、FCC 和 RTSP 的接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:476
msgid ""
"Default interface for all upstream traffic (multicast, FCC and RTSP). Leave "
"empty to use routing table."
msgstr "所有上游流量（组播、FCC 和 RTSP）使用的默认接口。留空则使用路由表。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:368
msgid "Edit the content of /etc/rtp2httpd.conf"
msgstr "编辑 /etc/rtp2httpd.conf 的内容"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:848
msgid ""
"Enable video snapshot feature. When enabled, clients can request snapshots "
"with snapshot=1 query parameter"
msgstr ""
"启用视频快照功能。启用后，客户端可以通过 snapshot=1 查询参数请求视频快照"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:616
msgid ""
"Enable zero-copy send with MSG_ZEROCOPY for better performance. Requires "
"kernel 4.14+ (MSG_ZEROCOPY support). On supported devices, this can improve "
"throughput and reduce CPU usage, especially under high concurrent load. "
"Recommended only when experiencing performance bottlenecks."
msgstr ""
"启用 MSG_ZEROCOPY 零拷贝发送以提升性能。需要内核 4.14+（支持 MSG_ZEROCOPY）。"
"在支持的设备上，可提升吞吐量并降低 CPU 占用，特别是在高并发负载下。建议仅在遇"
"到性能瓶颈时开启。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:337
msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "启用"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:640
msgid "External M3U"
msgstr "外部 M3U"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:652
msgid "External M3U Update Interval"
msgstr "外部 M3U 更新间隔"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:653
msgid ""
"External M3U automatic update interval in seconds (default: 7200 = 2 hours). "
"Set to 0 to disable automatic updates."
msgstr ""
"外部 M3U 自动更新间隔（秒），默认 7200（2 小时）。设为 0 禁用自动更新。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:603
msgid "FCC Listen Port Range"
msgstr "FCC 监听端口范围"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:871
msgid "FFmpeg Arguments"
msgstr "FFmpeg 参数"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:859
msgid "FFmpeg Path"
msgstr "FFmpeg 路径"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:641
msgid ""
"Fetch M3U playlist from a URL (file://, http://, https:// supported). "
"Example: https://example.com/playlist.m3u or file:///path/to/playlist.m3u"
msgstr ""
"从 URL 获取 M3U 播放列表（支持 file://、http://、https://）。示例：https://"
"example.com/playlist.m3u 或 file:///path/to/playlist.m3u"

#: root/usr/share/rpcd/acl.d/luci-app-rtp2httpd.json:3
msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-rtp2httpd"
msgstr "为 luci-app-rtp2httpd 授予 UCI 的访问权限"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:758
msgid "Hostname"
msgstr "主机名/域名"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:825
msgid "HTTP Proxy User-Agent"
msgstr "HTTP 代理 User-Agent"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:401
msgid "HTTP listen addresses. Use a bare port for all addresses (e.g., 5140), address:port for IPv4/hostnames, [IPv6]:port, or an absolute Unix socket path."
msgstr "HTTP 监听地址。使用裸端口表示监听所有地址（例如：5140），IPv4/主机名使用 address:port，IPv6 使用 [IPv6]:port，也可以使用 Unix socket 绝对路径。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:826
msgid ""
"Override the User-Agent header sent to upstream HTTP proxy requests. Leave "
"empty to forward the client User-Agent as-is."
msgstr ""
"覆盖发送给上游 HTTP 代理请求的 User-Agent 请求头。留空则按原样转发客户端的 "
"User-Agent。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:770
msgid ""
"If set, all HTTP requests must include r2h-token query parameter with "
"matching value (e.g., http://server:port/rtp/ip:port?fcc=ip:port&r2h-"
"token=your-token)"
msgstr ""
"设置后，所有 HTTP 请求必须携带 r2h-token 查询参数，且值与此配置匹配（例如："
"http://server:port/rtp/ip:port?fcc=ip:port&r2h-token=your-token）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:503
msgid ""
"Interface to use for FCC unicast upstream media stream (default: use routing "
"table)"
msgstr "用于 FCC 单播上游媒体流的接口（默认：使用路由表）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:516
msgid ""
"Interface to use for RTSP unicast upstream media stream (default: use "
"routing table)"
msgstr "用于 RTSP 单播上游媒体流的接口（默认：使用路由表）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:490
msgid ""
"Interface to use for multicast (RTP/UDP) upstream media stream (default: use "
"routing table)"
msgstr "用于组播（RTP/UDP）上游媒体流的接口（默认：使用路由表）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:604
msgid ""
"Local UDP port range for FCC client sockets (format: start-end, e.g., "
"40000-40100). Leave empty to use random ports."
msgstr ""
"FCC 客户端套接字使用的本地 UDP 端口范围（格式：起始端口-结束端口，例如："
"40000-40100）。留空则使用随机端口。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:449
msgid "Logging level"
msgstr "日志级别"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:541
msgid "Max clients allowed"
msgstr "最大客户端数"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:565
msgid ""
"Maximum number of buffers in zero-copy pool. Each buffer is 1536 bytes. "
"Default is 16384 (~24MB). Increase to improve throughput for multi-client "
"concurrency."
msgstr ""
"零拷贝缓冲池的最大缓冲区数量。每个缓冲区 1536 字节，默认 16384 个（约 "
"24MB）。增大此值以提高多客户端并发时的吞吐量。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:334
msgid "Monitoring & Advanced"
msgstr "监控与高级功能"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:590
msgid "Multicast Rejoin Interval"
msgstr "组播周期性重新加入间隔"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:332
msgid "Network & Performance"
msgstr "网络与性能"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:676
msgid "Note: The player page requires External M3U URL to be configured first."
msgstr "注意：播放器页面需要先配置外部 M3U URL 才能使用。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:552
msgid ""
"Number of worker processes. Set to 1 for resource-constrained devices, or "
"CPU cores for best performance."
msgstr ""
"工作进程数量。资源紧凑设备建议设置为 1，最佳吞吐量可以设置为 CPU 核心数。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:684
msgid "Open Player Page"
msgstr "打开播放器页面"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:716
msgid "Open Status Dashboard"
msgstr "打开状态面板"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:860
msgid ""
"Path to FFmpeg executable. Leave empty to use system PATH (default: ffmpeg)"
msgstr "FFmpeg 可执行文件的路径。留空则使用系统 PATH（默认：ffmpeg）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:591
msgid ""
"Periodic multicast rejoin interval in seconds (0=disabled, default 0). "
"Enable this (e.g., 30-120 seconds) if your network switches timeout "
"multicast memberships due to missing IGMP Query messages. Only use when "
"experiencing multicast stream interruptions."
msgstr ""
"周期性重新加入组播组的间隔时间（秒），0 表示禁用（默认 0）。如果您的网络交换"
"机因缺少 IGMP Query 消息而导致组播成员关系超时，可以启用此功能（建议 30-120 "
"秒）。仅在遭遇组播断流时需要启用。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:333
msgid "Player & M3U"
msgstr "播放器与 M3U"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:683
msgid "Player Page"
msgstr "播放器页面"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:665
msgid "Player Page Path"
msgstr "播放器页面路径"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:702
msgid "Please configure External M3U URL first"
msgstr "请先配置外部 M3U URL"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:400
msgid "Listen Addresses"
msgstr "监听地址"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:769
msgid "R2H Token"
msgstr "HTTP 请求认证令牌"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:347
msgid "Respawn"
msgstr "自动重启"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:781
msgid ""
"Set Access-Control-Allow-Origin header to enable CORS. Use * to allow all "
"origins, or specify a domain (e.g., https://example.com). Leave empty to "
"disable CORS."
msgstr ""
"设置 Access-Control-Allow-Origin 响应头以启用 CORS 跨域访问。设为 * 允许所有"
"来源，或指定域名（如 https://example.com）。留空则禁用 CORS。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:714
msgid "Status Dashboard"
msgstr "状态面板"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:726
msgid "Status Page Path"
msgstr "状态页面路径"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:577
msgid "UDP Receive Buffer Size"
msgstr "UDP 接收缓冲区大小"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:578
msgid ""
"UDP socket receive buffer size in bytes. Applies to multicast, FCC, and RTSP "
"sockets. Default is 524288 (512KB). For 4K IPTV streams at ~30 Mbps, 512KB "
"provides ~140ms of buffering. Increase to reduce packet loss. Note: actual "
"size may be limited by kernel parameter net.core.rmem_max."
msgstr ""
"UDP 套接字接收缓冲区大小（字节）。作用于组播、FCC、RTSP socket。默认 524288"
"（512KB）。对于 30 Mbps 的 4K IPTV 流，512KB 可提供约 140ms 的缓冲。增大此值"
"以减少丢包。注意：实际大小可能受内核参数 net.core.rmem_max 限制。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:666
msgid "URL path for the player page (default: /player)"
msgstr "播放器页面的 URL 路径（默认：/player）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:727
msgid "URL path for the status page (default: /status)"
msgstr "状态页面的 URL 路径（默认：/status）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:502
msgid "Upstream FCC Interface"
msgstr "上游 FCC 接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:475
msgid "Upstream Interface"
msgstr "上游接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:489
msgid "Upstream Multicast Interface"
msgstr "上游组播接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:515
msgid "Upstream RTSP Interface"
msgstr "上游 RTSP 接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:357
msgid "Use Config File"
msgstr "使用配置文件"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:358
msgid "Use config file instead of individual options"
msgstr "使用配置文件而不是单独的选项"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:103
msgid ""
"Use a bare port such as 5140 to listen on all addresses; *:5140 is not "
"supported here."
msgstr ""
"使用裸端口（如 5140）以监听所有地址；此处不支持 *:5140 的写法。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:109
msgid "Use port, address:port, hostname:port, [IPv6]:port, or an absolute Unix socket path, for example 5140, 192.168.1.1:8081, or /var/run/rtp2httpd.sock."
msgstr "请使用端口、address:port、hostname:port、[IPv6]:port 或 Unix socket 绝对路径，例如 5140、192.168.1.1 或 /var/run/rtp2httpd.sock。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:847
msgid "Video Snapshot"
msgstr "视频快照"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:759
msgid ""
"When configured, HTTP Host header will be checked and must match this value "
"to allow access. This value is also used as the hostname in M3U playlist "
"conversion. When using a reverse proxy, configure this with the proxied "
"access URL (including http(s):// and path prefix), e.g., https://my-domain."
"com/rtp2httpd, and ensure the reverse proxy forwards the Host header."
msgstr ""
"配置后将会检查 HTTP Host 头，必须匹配这里的值才能访问。M3U 转换时，也会使用这"
"个值来作为转换后节目地址的域名。使用反向代理时，需要配置为经过反向代理后的访"
"问地址（包括 http(s):// 和路径前缀），例如 https://my-domain.com/rtp2httpd，"
"并且需要反向代理透传 Host 头。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:792
msgid ""
"When enabled, uses HTTP X-Forwarded-For header as client address for status "
"page display. Only enable when running behind a reverse proxy."
msgstr ""
"启用后，将使用 HTTP X-Forwarded-For 头作为客户端地址，用于显示在状态面板上。"
"建议仅在使用反向代理时启用。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:551
msgid "Workers"
msgstr "工作进程数"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:791
msgid "X-Forwarded-For"
msgstr "X-Forwarded-For"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:615
msgid "Zero-Copy on Send"
msgstr "启用零拷贝发送"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:320
#: root/usr/share/luci/menu.d/luci-app-rtp2httpd.json:3
msgid "rtp2httpd"
msgstr "rtp2httpd"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:321
msgid ""
"rtp2httpd converts RTP/UDP/RTSP media into http stream. Here you can "
"configure the settings."
msgstr "rtp2httpd 用于将 RTP/UDP/RTSP 媒体流转换为 HTTP 流。在这里进行配置。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:528
msgid "Upstream HTTP Interface"
msgstr "上游 HTTP 接口"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:529
msgid ""
"Interface to use for HTTP reverse proxy upstream requests (default: use "
"routing table)"
msgstr "用于 HTTP 反向代理上游请求的接口（默认：使用路由表）"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:627
msgid "RTSP STUN Server"
msgstr "RTSP STUN 服务器"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:628
msgid ""
"When RTSP server only supports UDP transport and client is behind NAT, try "
"using STUN for NAT traversal (may not always succeed). Format: host:port or "
"host (default port 3478). Example: stun.miwifi.com"
msgstr ""
"当 RTSP 服务器仅支持 UDP 传输且客户端位于 NAT 后面时，尝试使用 STUN 进行 NAT "
"穿透（可能不总是成功）。格式：host:port 或 host（默认端口 3478）。示例："
"stun.miwifi.com"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:836
msgid "RTSP User-Agent"
msgstr "RTSP User-Agent"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:837
msgid ""
"User-Agent header used for upstream RTSP requests. Leave empty to use the "
"default rtp2httpd/{version}."
msgstr ""
"用于上游 RTSP 请求的 User-Agent 请求头。留空则使用默认的 rtp2httpd/{version}。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:814
msgid "Nginx-style access log format. Empty uses the default format. Supported variables include $client_addr, $time_iso8601, $service_url, $service_type and $upstream_url."
msgstr "Nginx 风格的访问日志格式。留空则使用默认格式。支持的变量包括 $client_addr、$time_iso8601、$service_url、$service_type 和 $upstream_url。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:737
msgid "Public mount path prefix for all rtp2httpd HTTP resources, for example /app/rtp2httpd."
msgstr "所有 rtp2httpd HTTP 资源的公开挂载路径前缀，例如 /app/rtp2httpd。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:746
msgid "Use Relative Paths in M3U"
msgstr "M3U 使用相对路径"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:747
msgid "When enabled, generated and rewritten M3U playlists omit the http://host prefix and use root-relative paths."
msgstr "启用后，生成和改写后的 M3U 播放列表会省略 http://host 前缀，并使用站点根相对路径。"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/rtp2httpd.js:804
msgid "Write one access log line for each media request. Leave empty to disable access logging."
msgstr "为每个媒体请求写入一行访问日志。留空则禁用访问日志。"